DESCRIPTION: A Cubit class that manages the counter state with increment and decrement methods. The cubit maintains a simple integer state starting at 0.
SOURCE: https://github.com/felangel/bloc/blob/master/docs/src/content/docs/tutorials/flutter-counter.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_1

