TITLE: Implementing CounterBloc in Dart
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of the CounterBloc class that handles increment and decrement events. The bloc maps CounterEvents to integer state values using Bloc library patterns.
SOURCE: https://github.com/felangel/bloc/blob/master/docs/src/content/docs/tutorials/ngdart-counter.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: dart
CODE:
```
import 'package:bloc/bloc.dart';

enum CounterEvent { increment, decrement }

class CounterBloc extends Bloc<CounterEvent, int> {
  CounterBloc() : super(0);

  @override
  Stream<int> mapEventToState(CounterEvent event) async* {
    switch (event) {
      case CounterEvent.increment:
        yield state + 1;
        break;
      case CounterEvent.decrement:
        yield state - 1;
        break;
    }
  }
}

```

