TITLE: Using BlocBuilder for Scoped Rebuilds in Flutter Bloc
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the recommended pattern of using BlocBuilder to scope rebuilds when state changes. This ensures only the necessary widgets are rebuilt when the bloc state changes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/felangel/bloc/blob/master/docs/src/content/docs/zh-cn/flutter-bloc-concepts.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: dart
CODE:
```
Widget build(BuildContext context) {
  return MaterialApp(
    home: Scaffold(
      body: BlocBuilder<MyBloc, MyState>(
        builder: (context, state) {
          //  Text
          return Text(state.value);
        },
      ),
    ),
  );
}
```

